assumes.post_str: The undersigned is directed to inform Members of the Council of Ministers that Shri assumed office as Cabinet Minister with effect from the forenoon of today the 14 th November 1956 He will hold charge of the Ministries of Heavy Industries and Commerce & Consumer Industries
